message:
@daniel @shay "Everyone, listen up, I just got off the phone with our biggest investor, Melon Tusk. He told me he was just trying to buy a Candle Holder for his grandma but the website wouldn't let him buy it.


Melon is really nervous because he heard about our outage earlier in the week.


Please tell me it's a problem with his computer and not a problem with our website." please check this reported issue and confirm if its from our end
